                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390204-name-1448" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390204-name-1448" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390204-name-1448" type="surname" value="GIBBONS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390204-name-1448" type="given" value="EDWIN"></interp>EDWIN GIBBONS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an omnibus proprietor, and live at Edmon<lb></lb>ton. My premises were broken open on the night of the 7th of January—they got in by breaking a square of glass and opening the window—I missed a flannel waistcoat which had been washed, and was hanging to dry on the horse, in the room that was broken into—this is it—(<hi rend="italic">looking at one</hi>)—I do not know the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. DOANE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> You are sure this is your waist<lb></lb>coat? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I missed this and a little girl's frock.</p>
